column5: Hello everyone,  Well, I have been gone for just over a month and man did I miss alot on this site. Lots of reading ahead for me  I haven't been on the site because I had to cancel internet because we were moving soon and I only just recently got it back up and running, Saturday.  Well the big day finally came, October 11 2007. That is when we took possesion of our new house   . We did our big move on the 20th and we had a house warming party on the following Saturday. Who knew that buying a new house would be so much work. This is my first free night so I decieded to check out the fishing community and see if everyone is still catching fish. And by the looks of things everyone still is  Well, I'm going to keep it short for now and I hope that everyone keeps on catching the fish.  Bye for now.
Welcome back!!!  It's been a bit ummm....cranky here lately....LOL.  Glad to hear the move went well....we'll do salmon next year!  Cliff
Congrats on the new house, I hope it all went smoothly   The work has just begun, but it's worth it  Maureen
Welcome back and congrates on the new house it will be one of the best investments you have made in life.   Art
Good luck with the new house!!
